title: VMWare ThinApp Enterprise 5.1.0.2079447 Portable [JUHAX69X]
description:
VMWare ThinApp Enterprise 5.1.0.2079447 Portable [JUHAX69X]
 
 
 
VMware ThinApp accelerates application deployment and simplifies
application migration with agentless application virtualization.
 
OS Migrations:
When migrating from Windows XP to Windows 7, migrate legacy web applications
that rely on Internet Explorer 6 by virtualizing IE6 along with the application.
 
Application Isolation:
Eliminate application conflicts by isolating applications from each other and the underlying
OS into a single executable file that can be easily deployed to many endpoints.
 
Server Consolidation:
Enable multiple applications and "sandboxed" user-specific configuration
data to reside safely on the same server.
 
Desktop Security:
Deploy ThinApp packages on "locked-down" PCs and allow end users to
run their favorite applications without compromising security.
 
Application Mobility:
Deploy, maintain, and update virtualized applications on USB flash drives for ultimate portability.
 
 
 
 
Portable: No installation needed. Extract 7-Zip file where ever You want, go in the folder and double click "setup_capture.exe". Create shortcut of it, if You want.
 
Pre-Cracked: No serials or cracks needed. Very easy and safe to start using or trying.
 
 
Why I have archived files in 7-Zip? Just to reduce the download size. Very effective with Portables.
 
I have test launched this once and seems to work. Scanned with Malwarebytes and F-Secure: Clean.
